Cyber Claw:




Cyber Claw, stopped and hovered. She stared at the ship that was unlike the 
ship that belonged to Megatron. It was Predacon base, so Injector told her. 
She thought to herself that the ship may have failed---but where did this 
one come from? She cocked her head, looking at it. She even wondered if it 
reconized her as the enemy. There was one way to find out.

She slowly flew forward, her feet a short distance from the ground. The 
auto-guns didn't target her. It may have reconized her signature. She went 
forward until she was inside. The looked around the interior. She couldn't 
remember the last time she was inside a Predacon vessel. She felt like a 
wild animal in a feral place. A part of her wanted out. Fast.
